0.7
	* Added a help document - Brian Pepple
	* Add background preferences - David Trowbridge
	* Add a plugin which intelligently disconnects/reconnects based on
	  network connection status via NetworkManager - David Trowbridge
	* Add an "OSD" plugin, which pops up important messages with libnotify - David Trowbridge
	* Implement "Save Transcript" - David Trowbridge
	* Add a plugin which sets away status based on screensaver state - Isak Savo
	* various and sundry bugfixes

0.6 "Braindome" (23 October 2005)
	* Set up a gnome url handler for irc:// links - Claessens Xavier
	* Add "ignore" to the user context menu - David Trowbridge
	* Add autoconnect and autojoin options in context menus - Guillaume Desmottes
	* Add nickname change dialog when clicking on the nick on the left of the input bar - Claessens Xavier
	* Add text and files drag and drop support - Guillaume Desmottes
	* Beginnings of command completion - David Trowbridge

